name: Interface CompilationUnitTree
text:
Represents the abstract syntax tree for compilation units (source
 files)
codes:
@Deprecated(since="11",
            forRemoval=true)
public interface CompilationUnitTree
extends Tree

methods.description: Return the list of source elements in this compilation unit.
Return the source name of this script compilation unit.
Returns if this is a ECMAScript "strict" compilation unit or not.

Returns the line map for this compilation unit, if available.
 Returns null if the line map is not available.

Return the ModuleTree associated with this compilation unit. This is null,
 if there is no module information from this compilation unit.
